{"tid":1002922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖遊戲！破關任務「自殺」　少女舉槍自轟慘死","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:09:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"259bc447d6ec0ab4aa627adaefd442fb95bde321","tid":1002922,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"曾於2017年在俄羅斯掀起自殺風潮的「藍鯨」（Blue Whale）遊戲又捲土重來！土耳其一名13歲少女因沉迷於該遊戲，在成功過關斬將到最後一刻時，接收到的任務竟是「自殺」，她便以父親的步槍自盡。警方目前正在調查此事是否與該遊戲相關。<br />\n《太陽報》報導，13歲的少女卡拉達（Emine Karadağ）於當地時間上周一（21日）被家人發現陳屍在家中的床上，生前更畫下鯨魚的圖像，並列出死前的自殺清單，以及藍鯨遊戲中的任何指示。警方更在案發現場發現一本筆記本，以「自殺是一種逃避」開頭的聲明，寫下「人生充滿痛苦，何以解憂，唯有一死」。<br />\n卡拉達的叔叔表示，起初她躺在床上，將子彈裝入父親的步槍接著自轟，我們看了她的筆記本，發現她在玩藍鯨遊戲，更在些紙上寫下遊戲要求每天必須做的事情，『我們會自殺、去天堂，然後復活、再次回來』，她完全被這個遊戲影響。」。警方目前正在調查此事是否與該遊戲相關。<br />\n據了解，藍鯨遊戲是一款俄羅斯的死亡遊戲，玩家落於10至14歲之間，且完全受控於看不見的遊戲管理者50種命令，通過簡訊發送指令和暴力圖片，鼓勵這些青少年玩家自殘，最後慢慢走上人生的絕路；目前已有130名俄羅斯青少年死於藍鯨遊戲。（邱奕欽／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190131/640_a5f27e6c7a2a5d84dd2c0a8463990495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190131%2F640_a5f27e6c7a2a5d84dd2c0a8463990495.jpg&h=025867c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190131/640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190131%2F640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg&h=4fea04ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a572a7dd9e49aeef9a42da720ba3ae45c46e7082","tid":1002922,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生前更畫下鯨魚的圖像<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190131/640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190131%2F640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg&h=4fea04ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9624b34e94b4b7cb8a6687ababe705d9d38465de","tid":1002922,"uid":34383,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"a572a7dd9e49aeef9a42da720ba3ae45c46e7082","tid":1002922,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生前更畫下鯨魚的圖像<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190131/640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190131%2F640_c529475910180c2edf77b62aebbc4e95.jpg&h=4fea04ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"海豚 同鯨魚都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788d32d9726f1134c1a054671aa8c0565cba2b66","tid":1002922,"uid":203543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:44:45.000Z","msg":"究竟個遊戲有咩魅力可以吸引咁多人沈迷? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e305628d99f0dfa72bcf99228fdfa1446f69a8","tid":1002922,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族支槍唔鎖？"},{"pid":"ee03ecc6c6280b1ddcc2721274776536d37416d3","tid":1002922,"uid":217452,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"邊到有得Download 隻game <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8927d21512a3b3465e8d713f32619f72ac02df2f","tid":1002922,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"俾個藉口自殺"},{"pid":"ebb44451b0e404289556019eddb366044254d540","tid":1002922,"uid":62532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"d人on9 瀨隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=